82
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,125
<b>[ - Get up.
- Come on. ]</b>

83
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,059
<b>[ - My goodness!
- Look at him! ]</b>

84
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:52,455
