88
00:07:01,570 --> 00:07:03,409
<b>[ It's so scary. ]</b>

89
00:07:03,410 --> 00:07:05,409
<b>[ I know, right? ]</b>

90
00:07:05,410 --> 00:07:06,505
<b>One moment.</b>

91
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,979
<b>- I'm sorry. Excuse me.
- You may not enter, sir.</b>

92
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,345
<b>- What's going on?
- I'm sorry.</b>

93
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:14,489
<b>Who are you?</b>

94
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:16,119
<b>I'm the patient's guardian. Please move.</b>

95
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,215
<b>I'm sorry, sir.</b>

96
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:47,545
<b>At 8:58 pm, Chairman Han Dong-gil</b>

97
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,945
<b>had passed away.</b>

98
00:07:54,530 --> 00:07:55,655
<b>What?</b>

99
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,425
<b>Move. Move!</b>

100
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,665
<b>Let go! Move!</b>

101
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:28,255
<b>[ Before Chairman Han passed away, ]</b>

102
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:31,199
<b>he left a will saying
he would like to inherit</b>

103
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:34,029
<b>the entire shares and management rights</b>

104
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:38,195
<b>to Managing Director Lim Chul-yong,
over here.</b>

105
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:42,405
<b>Who are you? Are you insane?</b>

106
00:08:43,170 --> 00:08:45,209
<b>My grandfather was unconscious
after the surgery.</b>

107
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:47,675
<b>[ And you're saying he suddenly
woke up and left a will? ]</b>

108
00:08:48,009 --> 00:08:49,475
<b>Do you expect me to believe that?</b>

109
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:52,545
<b>As the shareholders of Donghan Group,
I, Hong Dae-gon,</b>

110
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:55,019
<b>and Na Gyung-hun are the witnesses.</b>

111
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,285
<b>[ We were there. ]</b>

112
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:00,825
<b>As the family of the deceased,</b>

113
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,855
<b>[ my heart is breaking. ]</b>

114
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,195
<b>For our entire company,</b>

115
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:10,695
<b>I will gladly honor</b>

116
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:13,495
<b>Chairman Han Dong-gil's last will.</b>

117
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:17,475
<b>Lim Chul-yong...</b>

118
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,505
<b>Lim Chul-yong, you bastard.</b>

119
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:34,425
<b>[ Hey. ]</b>

120
00:09:34,690 --> 00:09:36,389
<b>Are you still working on
the bloodstain test</b>

121
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:38,799
<b>I asked from the fake registered car?</b>

122
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:42,199
<b>I told you. I'll contact you
once I get the results.</b>

123
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:45,039
<b>I'm going to send you
a DNA sample right now.</b>

124
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:47,465
<b>How much longer will it take
for you to run a lab test</b>

125
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:49,465
<b>and compare the two?</b>

126
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:52,335
<b>Are you okay?</b>

127
00:09:52,710 --> 00:09:54,345
<b>Were you hurt in any way?</b>

128
00:09:56,010 --> 00:09:57,615
<b>Goodness.</b>

129
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,115
<b>What is going on?</b>

130
00:10:01,650 --> 00:10:03,755
<b>Do you know how hard
I've been looking for you?</b>

131
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,815
<b>It's fine. Everything's fine.</b>

132
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:08,925
<b>Now that I've found you.</b>

133
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,395
<b>Goodness, gracious.</b>

134
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:25,435
<b>Dad, are you okay?</b>

135
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:27,445
<b>Yes, I'm fine.</b>

136
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:35,515
<b>Seol-a, you also get scars
when you fall down, right?</b>

137
00:10:36,090 --> 00:10:39,385
<b>This is just like that. So don't worry.</b>

138
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,155
<b>[ Seung-mo. ]</b>

139
00:10:44,430 --> 00:10:46,199
<b>According to Hyo-sook,</b>

140
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:49,995
<b>that lady who came for Byeol-na is a very
famous person in the fashion industry.</b>

141
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,735
<b>- Is that true?
- Yes.</b>

142
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,615
<b>[ Chef Moon Seung-mo ]</b>

143
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:16,855
<b>I can't believe Bella had lost her memory.</b>

144
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,095
<b>Anyway,</b>

145
00:11:22,130 --> 00:11:24,165
<b>thank you so much for everything
you have done for her.</b>

146
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:25,999
<b>I'd like to pay you
as an act of appreciation.</b>

147
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,605
<b>No, thank you.</b>

148
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,339
<b>But I'd like to ask why</b>

149
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:31,675
<b>you need to go to Seoul
with Byeol-na at this late hour.</b>

150
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:34,175
<b>I'm sorry, but I cannot allow this.</b>

151
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,785
<b>[ May I ask ]</b>

152
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:44,955
<b>in what relationship
the two of you are in?</b>

153
00:11:47,090 --> 00:11:48,325
<b>I'm...</b>

154
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:53,895
<b>Actually, I'm in no relations
with the Yu-jin who has found her memory.</b>

155
00:11:54,130 --> 00:11:55,965
<b>So you don't have to worry about us.</b>

156
00:11:58,270 --> 00:12:00,165
<b>I'll be honest with you</b>

157
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:03,135
<b>since you're telling me that.</b>

158
00:12:04,540 --> 00:12:06,635
<b>The man who got arrested earlier.</b>

159
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:09,105
<b>He's a worker at a security company</b>

160
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:11,049
