161
00:12:11,050 --> 00:12:12,175
<b>What?</b>

162
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:14,519
<b>Why did he...</b>

163
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:16,885
<b>I guess he had another client.</b>

164
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:19,215
<b>The conditions to kill her</b>

165
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:21,955
<b>must've been more appealing
than to find her.</b>

166
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:29,495
<b>Can you think of someone
who would possibly do that?</b>

167
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,535
<b>Lim Chul-yong</b>

168
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:34,565
<b>of Donghan International.</b>

169
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:40,035
<b>Mr. Lim Chul-yong?</b>

170
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,175
<b>If he's behind this,</b>

171
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:48,685
<b>why is he trying to kill Yu-jin?</b>

172
00:12:50,990 --> 00:12:54,155
<b>It'll take all night to explain that.</b>

173
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:57,799
<b>This place will be too dangerous to stay
once they find out</b>

174
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,159
<b>that their plans have fallen short.</b>

175
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,869
<b>We have to leave here now...</b>

176
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:03,225
<b>Leaving at this late hour
sounds more dangerous.</b>

177
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:06,735
<b>Anyway, since the hours are
too late right now,</b>

178
00:13:07,140 --> 00:13:09,035
<b>why don't you sleep here for tonight</b>

179
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,375
<b>and head out tomorrow after breakfast?</b>

180
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,125
<b>[ How many times
do I have to repeat myself? ]</b>

181
00:13:32,460 --> 00:13:34,165
<b>I did it by myself!</b>

182
00:13:35,530 --> 00:13:37,965
<b>Gosh, if you keep lying,</b>

183
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,269
<b>you're going to be in big trouble.</b>

184
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,309
<b>Goodness.</b>

185
00:13:41,310 --> 00:13:44,835
<b>I know your boss ordered you to do it.</b>

186
00:13:45,780 --> 00:13:48,049
<b>I'm talking about that man
who's your senior, Mr. Park.</b>

187
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:51,275
<b>Hey, that's extreme speculation.</b>

188
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,315
<b>[ Goodness. ]</b>

189
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:00,685
