200
00:14:44,770 --> 00:14:45,965
<b>Are you?</b>

201
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:50,165
<b>Gosh, how come I'm not hearing
anything from him?</b>

202
00:14:50,340 --> 00:14:51,675
<b>Hey, call him.</b>

203
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:54,379
