204
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:55,545
<b>Gosh.</b>

205
00:14:57,980 --> 00:14:59,445
<b>[ Oh Jung-tae ]</b>

206
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:04,615
<b>[ Mr. Jin ]</b>

207
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,725
<b>How did it go?</b>

208
00:15:10,830 --> 00:15:12,099
<b>Where are you?</b>

209
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:14,069
<b>What? Who are you?</b>

210
00:15:14,070 --> 00:15:15,199
