211
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:17,065
<b>We've met once before.</b>

212
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:19,569
<b>[ We've met at Mr. Park's desk last time. ]</b>

213
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:21,405
<b>I'm Officer Jo
from Nonyang Police Station.</b>

214
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,579
<b>I'm going to the village today
to see my father.</b>

215
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:27,975
