220
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,489
<b>I'll take care of things here.</b>

221
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:39,715
<b>You go out and get the car!</b>

222
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,595
<b>How did you end up being here?</b>

