<b>What?</b>

227
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:06,715
<b>I put on a show
without even knowing about it.</b>

228
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:11,215
<b>I was just trying to save you
and Belle Ombre.</b>

229
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,689
<b>- It was inevitable.
- And that's how</b>

230
00:16:13,690 --> 00:16:15,629
<b>you lost Belle Ombre?</b>

231
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:17,025
<b>To that fake?</b>

232
00:16:18,730 --> 00:16:20,895
<b>Do you know what your flaw is?</b>

233
00:16:21,430 --> 00:16:23,129
<b>You're too desperate.</b>

234
00:16:23,130 --> 00:16:25,695
<b>That's why you're always
being dragged around.</b>

235
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:29,235
<b>Belle Ombre isn't going to disappear
by not doing one show.</b>

236
00:16:29,310 --> 00:16:31,079
<b>How could you be so impatient</b>

237
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:33,075
<b>and think of doing a show with that fake?</b>

238
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:35,905
<b>I'm baffled.</b>

239
00:16:37,010 --> 00:16:38,249
<b>What about you?</b>

240
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:41,785
<b>Can't you think of it as a consequence
of not keeping in touch?</b>

241
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:43,549
<b>You should've told me</b>

242
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:46,019
<b>why you were going to Korea
and whom you were meeting.</b>

243
00:16:46,020 --> 00:16:48,229
<b>Why do you always have to do things
so selfishly?</b>

244
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:49,725
<b>Forget it.</b>

245
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:51,299
<b>Goodness.</b>

246
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:53,155
<b>So my boutique</b>

247
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:55,065
<b>is opening this weekend?</b>

248
00:16:55,230 --> 00:16:56,595
<b>Yes.</b>

249
00:16:58,040 --> 00:17:00,465
<b>Why do you ask? What are you going to do?</b>

250
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,105
<b>What do you think?</b>

251
00:17:03,210 --> 00:17:04,505
<b>I have to get back</b>

252
00:17:06,410 --> 00:17:07,805
<b>Belle Ombre.</b>

253
00:19:13,370 --> 00:19:16,605
<b>[ Sorry I left without saying goodbye. ]</b>

254
00:19:24,010 --> 00:19:27,745
<b>[ Thank you for everything, Chef Moon. ]</b>

255
00:19:36,930 --> 00:19:39,325
<b>[ Sorry I left without saying goodbye. ]</b>

256
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:44,695
<b>[ Thank you for everything, Chef Moon. ]</b>

257
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:49,135
<b>[ I thought I wouldn't be able to leave
if I had seen your face. ]</b>

258
00:19:49,970 --> 00:19:52,075
<b>[ So I'm saying goodbye
through the letter instead. ]</b>

259
00:19:54,950 --> 00:19:57,205
<b>[ This place was my grandfather's place. ]</b>

260
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,445
<b>[ Maybe that's why it was so cozy here. ]</b>

261
00:20:03,150 --> 00:20:05,685
<b>[ I think I will never be able to forget ]</b>

262
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:09,255
<b>[ the time I have spent with you. ]</b>

263
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,495
<b>[ Chef Moon. ]</b>

264
00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:16,165
<b>[ I wish ]</b>

265
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:20,365
<b>[ we can meet again ]</b>

266
00:20:23,810 --> 00:20:25,575
<b>[ after much time has passed. ]</b>

267
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:33,915
<b>[ Please say goodbye for me
to the people in the village. ]</b>

268
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,145
<b>[ I'm... ]</b>

269
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:40,929
<b>[ I'm sorry. ]</b>

270
00:20:40,930 --> 00:20:42,125
<b>[ I'm sorry. ]</b>

271
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:41,485
<b>This is so good!</b>

272
00:21:41,690 --> 00:21:43,249
<b>Pace yourself.</b>

273
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:45,515
<b>Drinks should be enjoyed
and appreciated, too.</b>

274
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,685
<b>This is just my second glass.</b>

275
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:50,025
<b>- You don't drink well, do you?
- Me?</b>

276
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:53,295
<b>Just take care of yourself after.</b>

277
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,565
<b>I don't plan on looking out for you.</b>

278
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:57,595
<b>- Fine.
- Fine.</b>

279
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:18,255
<b>[ So you're saying, you're in love? ]</b>

280
00:22:18,890 --> 00:22:21,425
<b>[ Don't say that in front of your dad,
okay? ]</b>

281
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:53,555
<b>- Great work, Byeol-na.
- Right?</b>

282
00:22:54,490 --> 00:22:56,225
<b>I'm telling you, I'm this good.</b>

283
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:27,855
<b>I'm sorry, Mom.</b>

284
00:23:29,530 --> 00:23:31,695
<b>[ I was so nearby, ]</b>

285
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,125
<b>but I couldn't remember.</b>

286
00:23:37,170 --> 00:23:38,335
<b>Mom.</b>

287
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:42,005
<b>No matter what happens,</b>

288
00:23:44,010 --> 00:23:45,775
<b>I will protect you.</b>

289
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:53,275
<b>[ - Yu-jin. ]
- Yes?</b>

290
00:23:53,620 --> 00:23:56,249
<b>- What are you doing?
- I was just drawing</b>

291
00:23:56,250 --> 00:24:01,129
<b>you and me on a stage.</b>

292
00:24:01,130 --> 00:24:02,425
<b>- Really?
- Yes.</b>

293
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:14,355
<b>Tell everyone
that they should be prepared.</b>

294
00:25:16,430 --> 00:25:21,305
<b>I'm going to meet every one of them</b>

295
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:24,505
<b>one by one.</b>

296
00:25:42,490 --> 00:25:44,799
<b>[ Good morning. ]</b>

297
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:47,399
<b>- Good morning.
- You are up early.</b>

298
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:49,395
<b>Are you wearing matching clothes?</b>

299
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:53,069
<b>I went downtown last night with Mom
and bought these.</b>

300
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:55,165
<b>- So put these on.
- Why?</b>

301
00:25:55,340 --> 00:25:57,339
<b>They are really expensive.</b>

302
00:25:57,340 --> 00:26:00,809
<b>Be careful not to spill kimchi juice
on it. That will be a disaster.</b>

303
00:26:00,810 --> 00:26:02,145
<b>She's right.</b>

304
00:26:02,180 --> 00:26:04,949
<b>You've got to show respect
to Designer Bella's clothing.</b>

305
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:07,619
<b>Are these clothes so great?</b>

306
00:26:07,620 --> 00:26:09,945
<b>Come to think of it, she's right.</b>

307
00:26:10,050 --> 00:26:13,189
<b>We must treat these clothes better.</b>

308
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:16,089
<b>The famous designer, Bella, made it.
We must treat them nicely.</b>

309
00:26:16,090 --> 00:26:17,025
<b>[ It's beautiful. ]</b>

310
00:26:17,690 --> 00:26:18,755
<b>[ She's right. ]</b>

311
00:26:19,060 --> 00:26:22,695
<b>So we have been hanging out
with a world-famous designer, Bella.</b>

312
00:26:22,770 --> 00:26:25,165
<b>- Yes.
[ - What do you mean by, "hang out"? ]</b>

313
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:26,865
<b>I even got</b>

314
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:31,165
<b>special lessons
from the famous designer, Bella.</b>

315
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:33,235
<b>[ - Goodness. ]
- Gosh.</b>

316
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:37,245
<b>Is Bella still asleep?</b>

317
00:26:37,380 --> 00:26:41,885
<b>The sun is high up.
Why haven't you come to work yet?</b>

318
00:26:43,250 --> 00:26:44,489
<b>Should I go and bring her?</b>

319
00:26:44,490 --> 00:26:46,189
<b>- Yes.
- Go ahead.</b>

320
00:26:46,190 --> 00:26:47,559
<b>Bella went to Seoul.</b>

321
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:48,985
<b>- What?
- What?</b>

322
00:26:50,030 --> 00:26:51,255
<b>She left.</b>

323
00:26:51,830 --> 00:26:53,025
<b>[ What did you say? ]</b>

324
00:26:56,670 --> 00:26:59,995
<b>What did you just say?
Is she not coming back?</b>

325
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:04,135
<b>[ How could she leave like that
without saying anything? ]</b>

326
00:27:04,980 --> 00:27:07,105
<b>She wouldn't do that to me.</b>

327
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,845
<b>I want to go to her.</b>

328
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:11,545
<b>[ You're not going anywhere! ]</b>

329
00:27:12,950 --> 00:27:15,215
<b>I'm going to go find her.</b>

330
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,655
<b>Seol-a.</b>

331
00:27:22,530 --> 00:27:25,395
<b>She got her memories back
and found her real family.</b>

332
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:29,495
<b>You should be happy for her.</b>

333
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:31,499
<b>But we are her family.</b>

334
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:32,669
<b>[ We are her family too. ]</b>

335
00:27:32,670 --> 00:27:33,799
<b>How could she leave like that</b>

336
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:35,965
<b>without saying anything?</b>

337
00:27:36,510 --> 00:27:39,575
<b>- Seol-a.
- This is just unfair!</b>

338
00:27:42,080 --> 00:27:44,575
<b>She's right.</b>

339
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:46,219
<b>Even if she got her memories back,</b>

340
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:48,515
<b>[ it's just rude that she left
without saying goodbye to us. ]</b>

341
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:50,245
<b>What a cold woman.</b>

342
00:27:51,390 --> 00:27:53,985
<b>It's not like we were going to stop her.</b>

343
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:56,685
<b>[ Come on. Don't be like that. ]</b>

344
00:27:57,060 --> 00:28:00,355
<b>Of course she can't walk around
the whole village in the early morning</b>

345
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:03,395
<b>and tell everyone that she's leaving.</b>

346
00:28:14,610 --> 00:28:15,805
<b>It's okay.</b>

347
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:52,115
<b>[ Deepest condolences for your loss ]</b>

348
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,419
<b>[ Prime Minister ]</b>

349
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:57,889
<b>[ Minister of Foreign Affairs ]</b>

350
00:28:57,890 --> 00:29:02,055
<b>[ Belle Ombre, Bella ]</b>

351
00:29:02,090 --> 00:29:04,085
<b>[ Junga Group ]</b>

352
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:08,025
<b>- Did you hear from Jin Tae-soo yet?
- Not yet, sir.</b>

353
00:29:08,730 --> 00:29:11,165
<b>Is the preparation of Bella Boutique
going all right?</b>

354
00:29:11,370 --> 00:29:14,065
<b>Yes, sir. It's going smoothly.</b>

355
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:16,005
<b>It'd better be good.</b>

356
00:29:16,710 --> 00:29:20,075
<b>We need to impress
the shareholders with that.</b>

357
00:29:20,810 --> 00:29:22,679
<b>We must show them</b>

358
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:25,615
<b>who is leading Donghan</b>

359
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,785
<b>and who is lining their pockets.</b>

360
00:29:29,220 --> 00:29:30,715
<b>I suppose that's why you decided to hold</b>

361
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:33,385
<b>the shareholders' meeting
after the Bella Boutique opening.</b>

362
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:35,689
<b>Let's finish up
both the appointment of the chairman</b>

363
00:29:35,690 --> 00:29:37,825
<b>and the merger with Bella Ombre</b>

364
00:29:38,660 --> 00:29:40,195
<b>at the meeting.</b>

365
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:42,325
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

366
00:29:43,130 --> 00:29:44,365
<b>You will be the chairman.</b>

367
00:29:46,870 --> 00:29:49,005
<b>Watch your mouth.</b>

368
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,005
<b>[ Hyun-a ]</b>

369
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:02,585
<b>[ Belle Ombre ]</b>

370
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:11,255
<b>Bella Boutique looks nice.</b>

371
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:13,425
<b>Focus on the launch of the boutique.</b>

372
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,825
<b>I'll look forward to the opening ceremony.</b>

373
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:28,675
<b>[ Opening Soon ]</b>

374
00:30:33,650 --> 00:30:35,485
<b>[ Belle Ombre, Bella ]</b>

375
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:46,755
<b>[ Belle Ombre, Bella ]</b>

376
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:52,535
<b>[ Bella, Bella ]</b>

377
00:31:58,210 --> 00:32:01,105
<b>Sir, I think you need to come in urgently.</b>

378
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,975
<b>I'm sorry for your loss.</b>

379
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,845
<b>Thank you...</b>

380
00:32:40,690 --> 00:32:42,089
<b>for coming.</b>

381
00:32:42,090 --> 00:32:44,455
<b>Of course I should come.</b>

382
00:33:08,650 --> 00:33:10,415
<b>You have been looking for me,</b>

383
00:33:11,150 --> 00:33:13,045
<b>but you don't seem so happy to see me.</b>

384
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:30,835
<b>Sir, that woman...</b>

385
00:33:31,140 --> 00:33:32,839
<b>Find Jin Tae-soo right now.</b>

386
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:34,465
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

387
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,785
<b>Finally, you two met.</b>

388
00:33:47,050 --> 00:33:48,745
<b>It's all thanks to you.</b>

389
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:50,355
<b>Please get in.</b>

390
00:34:01,430 --> 00:34:02,829
<b>It's not bad.</b>

391
00:34:02,830 --> 00:34:04,595
<b>Then we will proceed with it.</b>

392
00:34:05,170 --> 00:34:07,165
<b>Okay.</b>

393
00:34:07,670 --> 00:34:08,969
<b>Oh, right.</b>

394
00:34:08,970 --> 00:34:12,205
<b>This coat is the limited edition
prepared for the opening ceremony.</b>

395
00:34:12,210 --> 00:34:13,909
<b>Since it's a limited edition,</b>

396
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:16,305
<b>we will receive reservations
on a first-come-first-serve basis.</b>

397
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:20,019
<b>And there will also be your signing event
that will be like a celeb party.</b>

398
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:22,089
<b>[ The marketing team will
send you the schedule. ]</b>

399
00:34:22,090 --> 00:34:23,655
<b>Okay.</b>

400
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:27,429
<b>Can I have a look inside too?</b>

401
00:34:27,430 --> 00:34:28,755
<b>Sure. This way.</b>

402
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,904
<b>Hello. How may I help you?</b>

403
00:34:41,170 --> 00:34:43,679
<b>The store is not officially open yet.</b>

404
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:46,234
<b>I'm not a customer, so don't mind me.</b>

405
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:56,384
<b>[ This is it? ]</b>

406
00:34:56,490 --> 00:34:59,555
<b>The finale work from the fake gala show.</b>

407
00:35:01,130 --> 00:35:04,255
<b>It's the design you decided to ditch
three years ago.</b>

408
00:35:06,260 --> 00:35:07,895
<b>"Bella Boutique"...</b>

409
00:35:09,200 --> 00:35:10,335
<b>Then it needs to have</b>

410
00:35:11,139 --> 00:35:13,335
<b>proper Bella's design.</b>

411
00:35:25,750 --> 00:35:27,415
<b>It's been a while, Hyun-a.</b>

412
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:30,815
<b>[ Ms. Seo, can I have a word with you? ]</b>

413
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:32,155
<b>Yes, ma'am.</b>

414
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:51,335
<b>What's with the face?</b>

415
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:55,645
<b>You look like you saw someone
who has come back to life.</b>

416
00:35:57,850 --> 00:36:01,985
<b>Do you have any idea
what it is like to live</b>

417
00:36:02,450 --> 00:36:03,985
<b>as someone who is not yourself?</b>

418
00:36:06,060 --> 00:36:08,285
<b>I have done it, so I know what it's like.</b>

419
00:36:09,490 --> 00:36:12,495
<b>It's quite painful
when you wake up from the dream.</b>

420
00:36:14,930 --> 00:36:16,165
<b>I mean it.</b>

421
00:36:18,870 --> 00:36:20,405
<b>I will teach you what it's like soon.</b>

422
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:31,319
<b>Could you put it here?</b>

423
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,475
<b>Okay.</b>

424
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:37,115
<b>- Let me do it.
- Thanks.</b>

425
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,629
<b>Is there anything else
I can help you with?</b>

426
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:48,065
<b>This should be enough for the work.</b>

427
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,529
<b>That's a relief.</b>

428
00:36:49,530 --> 00:36:51,465
<b>Just to be safe,</b>

429
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:54,565
<b>we've hired private security guards
to guard you two at all times.</b>

430
00:36:54,870 --> 00:36:58,309
<b>We'll make sure that you're safe here,</b>

431
00:36:58,310 --> 00:36:59,479
<b>[ so don't worry too much. ]</b>

432
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,849
<b>[ Thank you for all of this. ]</b>

433
00:37:01,850 --> 00:37:05,249
<b>[ Well, it was Mr. Kang
and Ms. Han's orders, ]</b>

434
00:37:05,250 --> 00:37:06,685
<b>[ so don't feel too overwhelmed. ]</b>

435
00:37:08,090 --> 00:37:11,485
<b>[ I hear that she lost her memory
and got it back just now? ]</b>

436
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:15,185
<b>[ I guess that's why she was at Chef Moon's
all along. ]</b>

437
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:16,625
<b>What kind</b>

438
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:22,025
<b>of a person is this Chef Moon Seung-mo?</b>

439
00:37:22,970 --> 00:37:25,369
<b>He's one of the greatest chefs in Korea.</b>

440
00:37:25,370 --> 00:37:28,165
<b>He's currently working with Donghan Food.</b>

441
00:37:29,370 --> 00:37:30,575
<b>I see.</b>

442
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:35,379
<b>Give me a call anytime
if you need anything.</b>

443
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:37,475
<b>- Thank you so much.
- Bye then.</b>

444
00:37:38,850 --> 00:37:39,945
<b>Let's go.</b>

445
00:37:45,690 --> 00:37:46,825
<b>[ Bella. ]</b>

446
00:37:55,170 --> 00:37:59,395
<b>Do you think we can pull it through?
We've got less than four days.</b>

447
00:37:59,470 --> 00:38:02,105
<b>Why? Are you worried
that my taste is gone?</b>

448
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:04,535
<b>That's not what I'm saying.</b>

449
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:07,279
<b>I'm talking about your health.</b>

450
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,745
<b>Don't worry about it. You can get going.</b>

451
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:12,145
<b>And this.</b>

452
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:16,285
<b>If you need anything, just call me.</b>

