00:46:55,070 --> 00:46:56,535
<b>I'll be back soon.</b>

535
00:46:56,740 --> 00:46:58,335
<b>Drive safe.</b>

536
00:47:24,140 --> 00:47:26,499
<b>What a master plan this late at night.</b>

537
00:47:26,500 --> 00:47:28,669
<b>I'm sorry to have you go through
