<b>wouldn't have happened.</b>

554
00:51:15,030 --> 00:51:18,939
<b>[ I'm anorexic, so I can't eat properly, ]</b>

555
00:51:18,940 --> 00:51:21,165
<b>and I'm very sensitive,</b>

556
00:51:21,810 --> 00:51:24,435
<b>so I can never live
