00:55:16,270 --> 00:55:17,709
<b>Let me help!</b>

582
00:55:17,710 --> 00:55:20,075
<b>I don't know...</b>

583
00:55:20,480 --> 00:55:23,049
<b>- Say something!
- Why don't we...</b>

584
00:55:23,050 --> 00:55:24,375
<b>Wait!</b>

585
00:55:24,820 --> 00:55:26,919
<b>Let's get changed first.</b>

586
00:55:26,920 --> 00:55:29,485
<b>- That's a great idea.
- Let's go!</b>

587
00:56:00,950 --> 00:56:02,519
<b>Welcome to</b>

588
00:56:02,520 --> 00:56:04,489
<b>- Pungcheonok!
- Pungcheonok!</b>

589
00:56:04,490 --> 00:56:06,615
<b>[ - Thank you. ]
- Sir.</b>

590
00:56:07,020 --> 00:56:10,525
<b>This is the famous restaurant
that I've been telling you about.</b>

591
00:56:10,660 --> 00:56:13,195
<b>Pungcheonok, that's a great name.</b>

592
00:56:20,100 --> 00:56:22,035
<b>- We're ready to order.
